<scroll-view class="page-scroll" scroll-y>
  <view class="floating-orb floating-orb--top"></view>
  <view class="floating-orb floating-orb--bottom"></view>
  <view class="page-shell settlement-page">
    <view class="settlement-card">
      <view class="section-title">
        <view class="section-heading">最终付款指令</view>
        <view class="chip-pill">服务端算法位</view>
      </view>
      <view class="plan-list">
        <view class="soft-cell plan-item" wx:for="{{plans}}" wx:key="index">
          <view>
            <view class="plan-item__title">{{item.from}} → {{item.to}}</view>
            <view class="muted">建议直接微信 / 支付宝转账</view>
          </view>
          <view class="plan-item__amount stat-positive">¥{{item.amount}}</view>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="soft-cell tea-item">
        <view>
          <view class="plan-item__title">茶水账户独立结算</view>
          <view class="muted">公共费用不并入玩家个人净输赢</view>
        </view>
        <view class="plan-item__amount">¥{{teaFeeAmount}}</view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="panel-card">
      <view class="section-title">
        <view class="section-heading">结算摘要</view>
        <view class="pill-text">总盈亏 {{totalAbsProfit}}</view>
      </view>
      <view class="muted settlement-copy">
        这一步建议由服务端统一执行轧差算法。当前前端展示的是可交互的 MVP 方案，便于后续直接对接接口和 WebSocket 房间事件。
      </view>
      <view class="popup-actions">
        <t-button theme="primary" block bind:tap="handleOpenConfirm">确认解散并归档</t-button>
        <t-button theme="default" variant="outline" block bind:tap="handleGoBack">暂不结算</t-button>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <t-dialog
    visible="{{confirmVisible}}"
    title="确认房间结算"
    content="归档后会将当前房间写入历史记录，并重置成新的记账房间。"
    confirmBtn="确认归档"
    cancelBtn="再想想"
    bind:confirm="handleConfirmArchive"
    bind:cancel="handleCloseConfirm"
    bind:close="handleCloseConfirm"
  />

  <app-tabbar value="room" />
</scroll-view>
